OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud
OL,6,Fbreaking up a little during the
OL,7,Fevening to bring some late sunshine.
OL,8,FThicker cloud in the south tonight
OL,9,Fwith the odd spot of rain. Turning
OL,10,Fchilly under the clear spells in the
OL,11,Feast, mild in the west.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FA few early showers possible
OL,14,Fin the south, but a drier and brighter
OL,15,Fstart elsewhere. Turning cloudier into
OL,16,Fthe afternoon and dry. Feeling warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
