OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FSpells
OL,6,Fof rain possible at times over the
OL,7,Fnext few days, but some drier,
OL,8,Fbrighter and warmers intervals in
OL,9,Fbetween. Feeling warmer and more
OL,10,Fhumid, especially overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
